name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Do I Make You Randy Baby Yeah

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Change horny to randy baby yeah!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Sometimes a word has so much weight and significance that it becomes a joke in itself. Sometimes that word becomes overly used to a point where even its ironic use becomes tiring. Sometimes you just find the word randy very, very funny. 

Replace horny with randy, baby yeah.
